@{" Username             " link term_phone_gads_8} - Username in der Mailbox
@{" Passwort             " link term_phone_gads_9} - Passwort in der Mailbox

@{" Modem-Konfig         " link term_phone_gads_10} - Modem- & Terminal-Konfig
